<div class="cards-container">
  <!-- Donate Cards: Furniture Donation Locations -->
  <div class="card" data-category="Donate">
    <h2>Pass-It-On (Online Platform)</h2>
    <p><strong>Address:</strong> Online platform for donating usable furniture and household items to those in need in Singapore.</p>
    <p><strong>Services:</strong> Connects donors with Voluntary Welfare Organisations and individuals in need. Large items like furniture can be matched to requests.</p>
    <p><strong>Contact:</strong> <a href="https://www.passiton.org.sg/" target="_blank">passiton.org.sg</a></p>
    <p><strong>Distance:</strong> N/A (Online)</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card" data-category="Donate">
    <h2>MINDS Shop Plus @ Hougang</h2>
    <p><strong>Address:</strong> 11 Hougang Ave 6, #01-02, Singapore 538789</p>
    <p><strong>Services:</strong> Accepts pre-loved furniture, household items, and more. Proceeds support persons with intellectual disabilities.</p>
    <p><strong>Contact:</strong> 8180 1760</p>
    <p><strong>Distance:</strong> Hougang</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card" data-category="Donate">
    <h2>The Salvation Army - Donation In Kind Booths</h2>
    <p><strong>Address:</strong> Multiple locations (e.g., 356 Tanglin Road, Singapore 247674)</p>
    <p><strong>Services:</strong> Accepts furniture, household items, and more. Items in good condition are resold to support community programs.</p>
    <p><strong>Contact:</strong> 1800-227-1183</p>
    <p><strong>Distance:</strong> Various</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card" data-category="Donate">
    <h2>HDB Upcycling Corner</h2>
    <p><strong>Address:</strong> Various HDB Town Councils (check with your local Town Council)</p>
    <p><strong>Services:</strong> Accepts reusable furniture and household items for upcycling or redistribution.</p>
    <p><strong>Contact:</strong> Check with your Town Council</p>
    <p><strong>Distance:</strong> Various</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card" data-category="Donate">
    <h2>Blessings in a Bag</h2>
    <p><strong>Address:</strong> 2 Pandan Valley, #01-206, Singapore 597626</p>
    <p><strong>Services:</strong> Occasionally accepts furniture and household items for families in need (check website for current needs).</p>
    <p><strong>Contact:</strong> <a href="https://www.blessingsinabag.org/" target="_blank">blessingsinabag.org</a></p>
    <p><strong>Distance:</strong> Pandan Valley</p>
  </div>
